---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const focus = [
  'Cloud cost governance and FinOps visibility',
  'Infrastructure automation and runbook elimination',
  'Certificate and expiry-risk management tooling',
  'Cross-cloud operational dashboards for Azure and AWS',
  'Control workflows for remediation and ownership tracking',
  'Integration with Microsoft ecosystem and ITSM layers',
];
---

<Layout
  title="Cloud Infrastructure Tooling"
  description="RePass Cloud builds cloud governance tooling for Azure and AWS including FinOps visibility, automation workflows, and operational control layers."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow"><i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up"></i> Service line</div>
      <h1>Cloud infrastructure tooling</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        We build practical cloud tooling for teams that need real operational visibility and governance,
        not another disconnected dashboard.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="showcase-split">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Core delivery areas</div>
          <h2>Control over cost, risk, and cloud operations</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            Cloud complexity compounds quickly across accounts, teams, and providers. We implement the control
            layer that unifies signals, actions, and ownership.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-trust" style="margin-top:1rem;">
            {focus.map((item) => (
              <div class="hero-trust-item"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle"></i> {item}</div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-panel">
          <div class="section-label">Typical environments</div>
          <h3>Azure + AWS + Microsoft estate integration</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Most clients run hybrid realities. We build systems that bridge cloud provider controls
            with enterprise identity, service desks, and financial governance processes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);">Engage</div>
      <h2>Need stronger cloud governance without adding operational sprawl?</h2>
      <p>Show us your cloud operating pain points and we will map a pragmatic tooling roadmap.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Talk to us <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
